HEADWORD: Streetward
<hw>Street"ward`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An officer, or
ward, having the care of the streets.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Cowell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

