HEADWORD: Streetward
<hw>Street"ward</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Facing toward the
street.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Their little <qex>streetward</qex> sitting room.</q>
<rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
